details.name: Arcane Bolt
details.description: Skywrath Mage launches a slow-moving bolt of arcane magic, dealing damage to an enemy unit based on Skywrath Mage's intelligence.
details.upgrade_description: When Skywrath Mage casts Arcane Bolt, a different random target within %scepter_radius% range willl be hit with the same ability. Heroes will take priority.
